   ___PLOT SUMMARY___
   Ben Archer is not happy. His mother, Sandy, has just met a man, and it looks
   like things are pretty serious. Driven by a fear of abandonment, Ben tries
   anything and everything to ruin the "love bubble" which surrounds his mom.
   However, after Ben and Jack's experiences in the Indian Guides, the two
   become much closer.
